OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with a few showers, but
OL,7,Fa few clear spells. Overnight will be
OL,8,Fmainly dry, but still la few patches
OL,9,Fof light rain. Mostly light easterly
OL,10,Fwinds but breezy near the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA dry and settled day with
OL,13,Fmostly light winds.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHigh
OL,16,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,17,Fsettled few days with light winds.
OL,18,FCloudy at times, especially in the
OL,19,Fnorth and east but still plenty of
OL,20,Fbright and sunny spells.
